bill.summary: 6/10/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to extend, through December 31, 1996, the suspension of duty on: (1) 4-chloro-2-nitroaniline; (2) 4-chloro,5-dimethoxyaniline; (3) 3,4-diaminophenetole, dihydrogen sulfate; and (4) 6-hydroxy-2-napthoic acid.
